{"tid":1223884,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"6.16 HKers Assemble!!!","createTime":"2019-06-14T22:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T11:52:06.000Z","uid":229621,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dd613ea3a41cba16288f0704ab02db34f804ac36","tid":1223884,"uid":229621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T22:47:43.000Z","msg":"發夢星期三食左好多椒 個人冷靜落黎之後充滿無力感<br />\n不斷問自己可以做到啲咩 幫到啲咩<br />\n<br />\n星期日既宣傳嚴重不足 想係依度著手<br />\n所以揾埋朋友整左幅圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SJd2Jzv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSJd2Jzv.jpg&h=547e4e8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁岩最近學左photoshop 嘗試將佢p落唔同既地方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4tdqGQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4tdqGQQ.jpg&h=09b20995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田站行人天橋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Cs3tmU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Cs3tmU.jpg&h=abf98615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九龍塘站天橋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gPqD1Hi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgPqD1Hi.jpg&h=4185f23f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n城大<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Gf8Et7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Gf8Et7.jpg&h=b5276e1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅磡天橋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFepXfY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFepXfY.jpg&h=70add97d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尖沙咀見到有其他人已自發ps左 (但轉個頭俾人摵左 所以一定要人海戰術)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G3iY1Jb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG3iY1Jb.jpg&h=23321a69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紅磚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gHKpXgG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgHKpXgG.jpg&h=556a73df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣天橋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pbyqGKr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpbyqGKr.jpg&h=99e54930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n荃灣站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nB17U4B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnB17U4B.jpg&h=06ac7727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彌敦道<br />\n<br />\n發夢時間/資源有限<br />\n今次除左想叫多啲人出黎 亦想其他本身諗住出黎既人行多一步向身邊既人宣傳<br />\n<br />\n星星之火 可以燎原<br />\n<br />\n6.16<br />\nHKers Assemble!!!"},{"pid":"984f90070a70cde9ac9ed98abb1119da06ea151c","tid":1223884,"uid":229621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T22:55:44.000Z","msg":"由岩岩諗到直到出post為時10個鐘<br />\n加上好多野都係第一次試<br />\n未係做到最好 請見諒<br />\n只係想講<br />\n大家不要忽視自己既力量!"},{"pid":"d7ac61d75296d3eec5b5989e76e6a2cfb7d1f9ae","tid":1223884,"uid":229621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:11:35.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"951faa2467c62665eb2b8af7d80ca4afbabb7c83","tid":1223884,"uid":229621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T23:12:41.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"79c4e94a1c2ebab16b5009cfac5289605b5ca366","tid":1223884,"uid":229621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:18:53.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"393a0f3253e0217e7abc75132a5577c8568e8cb1","tid":1223884,"uid":229621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T07:46:43.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"a536e3cb10a355f512ce5636f5c31c737153b122","tid":1223884,"uid":229621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T08:00:50.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"0db94f5aa25e45637fa2d4feea81e5a3d1e75b36","tid":1223884,"uid":229621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:21:32.000Z","msg":"推!!!"},{"pid":"804484843c2bf5640483dc272633e5e762fc7220","tid":1223884,"uid":229621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8DtRGB6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=